# Ryu Island (apps/island) — environment configuration
#
# Electron companion: Shadow context monitoring, proactive suggestions, and a
# mini chat onto Core. Most settings persist in Electron userData; these env
# vars are optional overrides for local dev and headless testing.
#
# EVERYTHING here is OPTIONAL — Island runs with sensible defaults on install.

# Core bearer token when Core auth is enabled (RYU_TOKEN on the node). Falls
# back to the value saved in island-services.json when unset.
# RYU_TOKEN=

# Dev-only: Vite HMR renderer URL. When set, windows load this instead of the
# packaged renderer HTML (electron-vite sets this during `bun run dev`).
# ELECTRON_RENDERER_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Enable verbose proactive-engine debug logging in the main process.
# ISLAND_DEBUG=1
